The paper deals with privacy-preserving machine learning, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also focuses on deep neural networks, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper involves computations and optimization, which can be categorized under distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). The paper also involves cryptography, which can be categorized under computer engineering (cs.CE). Finally, the paper deals with smart applications, which can be categorized under control systems and robotics (cs.SY).
